<blockquote>
<p>The enemy of my enemy is my friend.</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>Keep your friends close, and your enemies closer.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>This is my gift for <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/raptie" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1968091); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1968091&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609264634" alt="Raptie" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1968091)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/raptie" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1968091); return false;">Raptie</a></span> for the 2020 Wiki Christmas art exchange. I was given two choices for my gift, and I went with the much more ambitious one.</p>
<p>Thank you to</p>
<ul>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1613974); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1613974&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609264634" alt="UraniumEmpire" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1613974)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1613974); return false;">UraniumEmpire</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609264634" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;">Uncle Nicolini</a></span> for their feedback and critique.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/raptie" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1968091); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1968091&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609264634" alt="Raptie" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1968091)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/raptie" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1968091); return false;">Raptie</a></span> for the initial idea.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1581620); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609264634" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1581620); return false;">DarkStuff</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/elogee-fishtruck" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4037075); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4037075&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609264634" alt="Elogee FishTruck" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4037075)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/elogee-fishtruck" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4037075); return false;">Elogee FishTruck</a></span> for organizing the Art Exchange.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jakdragonx" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5588260); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5588260&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609264634" alt="JakdragonX" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5588260)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jakdragonx" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5588260); return false;">JakdragonX</a></span> for the positive review given in the Art Exchange thread.</li>
<li>And you reading this, should you decide to turn this lofty premise into a canon!</li>
</ul>
<p>Note: The Global Occult Coalition are not part of the United Nations in this tale.</p>

