														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4856960">
									

<blockquote>
<p>This is an astonishing GOC article that flips the Foundation on-top of its head. First, the content warning: please heed it. Okay, going into the article itself: I'm blown away. This concept, just on its face, has so much potential. I love the idea behind the Foundation just being a rag-tag conglomeration of all the GoI's unilaterally hating the Coalition. &quot;Keep your enemies closer,&quot; and all of that. I love the detail and synopsis of each of the Bellfather members. You can tell that a ton of time has been reserved for figuring out how to implement the differing characters and their involvement with the Foundation's directive. The format that it follows with the messages really helps the reader follow along with the article, with the ending being just so captivating. Seriously people, expand upon this. Characterizing the Overwatch Command like this could really lead to so much more good content. It also kinda revitalizes the &quot;Foundation is evil&quot; vibe that I've always digged. Good, good job author!</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Forwarding my original review from the Thread onto here. Nothing else to say or critique. This is legitimately wonderful :)</p>

